# Frontend build-time env (Vite). Copy to interface/.env to override.
# Only VITE_-prefixed vars are exposed to the browser bundle.
#
# Absolute base URL for the JSON API. Baked in at build time. Leave unset to use
# the defaults: "/" (same-origin) in the browser, the sidecar loopback
# http://127.0.0.1:8080 in the Tauri desktop shell. See docs/api-endpoint.md.
# Set it to retarget a build, e.g. point a browser build at a remote API
# (CORS + https required when cross-origin — see docs/api-endpoint.md):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.example.com
